ha","tag-recommendation-al-mustahab","tag-sharia","tag-singing"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8Of","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":25260,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/10\/nikah-secret-marriage-invalid\/","url_meta":{"origin":33867,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Nikah: Declare marriage in public, not in secret","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 10, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAnnounce this marriage publicly, conduct it in the mosque, and strike the drums for it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1089 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Zurqani Ibn Taymiyyah said, \"Malik obligated announcing the marriage. A secret marriage is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8733,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/23\/entertainment-wedding-ansar\/","url_meta":{"origin":33867,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Entertainment: The Prophet entertains Ansar for a wedding","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 23, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: She prepared a lady for marriage to a man among the Ansar. The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Aisha, do you have any entertainment? Verily, the Ansar are fond of entertainment.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4868 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Badr al-Din al-'Ayni said, \"The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25926,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/15\/halal-nikah-public-secret-marriage\/","url_meta":{"origin":33867,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: Lawful marriage must be announced publicly","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 15, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Hatib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe difference between an unlawful and lawful marriage is the beating of drums and raising of voices.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1088 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani Abu Bakr Abdul Aziz said, \u201cA secret marriage\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33777,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/16\/minimum-valid-marriage\/","url_meta":{"origin":33867,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nikah: Minimum legal requirements for valid marriage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no marriage unless with a guardian and two credible witnesses. Any marriage contracted with less than that is invalid. If there is a dispute, the ruler is the guardian for one without a guardian.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25924,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/15\/secret-marraige-zina\/","url_meta":{"origin":33867,"position":4},"title":"Umar on Zina: Secret marriage is a type of adultery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 15, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Zubayr reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, was presented with a marriage which no one had witnessed but one man and one woman. Umar said, \u201cThis is a secret marriage and I do not permit it. If I had known of it beforehand, I would\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33162,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/10\/umar-inbreeding-marriage-cousins\/","url_meta":{"origin":33867,"position":5},"title":"Umar on Inbreeding: Do not to marry within bloodlines, close cousins","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Mulaykah reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said to the house of Al-Sa\u2019ib, \u201cYou have become frail, so marry intelligent people unrelated to you.\u201d Al-Shafi\u2019i said, \u201cWhenever the people of a household do not allow their women to marry men outside of their line,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33867","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=33867"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33867\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=33867"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=33867"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=33867"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}